# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Section B: Build cache + test/stress/local-validation artifacts
# Sprint 6 add — keep agent context lean (ripgrep respects these).
# Patterns without leading "/" match at any depth — single-line entries
# cover worker/, web/, e2e/ sub-directories. Avoid path-prefix triplets.
# Already-existing-rule coverage notes:
#   dist/        — generic, catches worker/dist AND web/dist AND root /dist
#   site/        — generic, catches site/.astro build cache transitively
#   node_modules/ — caught at root
#   .wrangler/   — catches worker/.wrangler transitively (no separate rule)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# TypeScript incremental build cache (regenerated on tsc).
*.tsbuildinfo

# Playwright HTML report + raw test artifacts (regenerated on test run).
playwright-report/
test-results/

# Test coverage HTML report (regenerated on `npm test -- --coverage`).
coverage/

# Stress-test run outputs (each run creates a new dated directory).
stress-results/
stress/results/
worker/scripts/e2e-uat-output*/

# Local-validation scratch sessions (AI Vision manual trace, ad-hoc curl).
# Note: *.tmp intentionally NOT added — over-broad, no observed .tmp source
# files in workflow. Scratch dirs are scoped to worker/ and web/ only.
worker/scratch/
web/scratch/
